This paper deals with Natural Language Processing (NLP) and specifically focuses on improving lexical entailment. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also discusses the use of supervised learning and vector space models, which are common in machine learning and artificial intelligence (cs.LG and cs.AI). Additionally, the paper mentions the use of clustering, which is a common technique in information retrieval (cs.IR) and unsupervised learning (cs.SI).
